metadata.name: Anubis
metadata.description:
I had gone to a very far time and place.
I saw a creature, who had been frozen there for a long time.
One night, They appeared in the sky .They woke him up, named him Anubis and sent him to The Blue Planet.

Video & Music created by Ali Saboohi.
The main softwares used : Cinema 4D(video) + Adobe Photoshop (To make the textures used in the video) + FL Studio (Music "without using any ready samples" )
